data.description: Welcome home to this cozy 3 BR 2.5BA home in Griffin Park. The open Living and Dining Room Combo has wood laminate flooring and is perfect for entertaining. Kitchen has stainless appliances and granite countertops. All bedrooms are located upstairs. The master bedroom is spacious with trey ceiling, and his and hers closets. The property has a private back yard and is located next door to the Community Pool and Playground.
